	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title">Digital Tools Overview</h1>
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Hesperian now offers a variety of digital tools for health promotion, designed for people with limited computer or internet access. Each tool represents thousands of hours of writing, production, field testing, translation, and digital adaptation. Taken together, they form the Hesperian Digital Commons, a collaborative project to re-imagine our trusted print materials through the innovative use of technology.</p>
<h2><a href="https://hesperian.org/books-and-resources/">Trusted Health Information</a></h2>
<p><a href="/books-and-resources/#ui-tabs-1"><img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-8861" title="wiki_simpler" src="https://hesperian.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/wiki_simpler-150x150.png" alt="" width="65" height="65" /></a><em>Immediate online access</em>: The <a href="http://en.hesperian.org/w/index.php?title=Healthwiki">HealthWiki</a> provides content in a flexible, wiki-based format — well suited for low or intermittent networks. The HealthWiki facilitates online searches by topic and across multiple languages.</p>
<p><em><a href="http://store.hesperian.org/HB/prod/E010.html"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-9646" title="ebook icon wordpress" src="https://hesperian.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/ebook-icon-wordpress.png" alt="" width="65" height="63" /></a>Re</em><em>ad on a tablet</em>: <a href="http://store.hesperian.org/prod/Where_There_Is_No_Doctor.html"><em>Where There Is No Doctor</em></a>,<em> <a href="http://store.hesperian.org/prod/Recruiting_the_Heart_Training_the_Brain.html">Recruiting the Heart, Training the Brain</a></em>, and our three environmental health booklets (<a href="http://store.hesperian.org/prod/Sanitation_and_Cleanliness.html"><em>Sanitation and Cleanliness for a Healthy Environment</em></a>; <em><a href="https://store.hesperian.org/prod/Pesticides_are_Poison.html">Pesticides are Poison</a></em>; and <em><a href="http://store.hesperian.org/prod/Water_for_Life.html">Water for Life</a></em>) are now available as Ebooks! </p>
<p><a href="/books-and-resources/"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-8576" title="AdobePDFicon" src="https://hesperian.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/AdobePDFicon2.png" alt="" width="65" height="65" /></a><em>Download health information</em>: Our books continue to be available for <a href="/books-and-resources/">free PDF download.</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><a href="https://hesperian.org/books-and-resources/language-list/">Multi-lingual Resources</a></h2>
<p>Hesperian publishes books in English and Spanish, and independent organizations <a href="/books-and-resources/language-list/"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-8871" title="AR_lang_icon" src="https://hesperian.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/AR_lang_icon.png" alt="" width="65" height="55" /></a>have translated Hesperian materials into an astounding 88 languages. Many of those materials are now available through Hesperian’s online <a title="Resources By Language" href="/books-and-resources/language-list/">language pages</a>. We offer:</p>
<ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>print books in 12 languages</li>
<li>free PDFs in 34 languages</li>
<li>HealthWiki content in 18 languages </li>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
<h2><a href="https://hesperian.org/books-and-resources/our-mobile-applications/">Our Mobile Applications</a></h2>
<p><strong>Now</strong><a href="/books-and-resources/safe-pregnancy-and-birth-mobile-app/"><img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-4804 alignleft" title="Preg Icon App" src="https://hesperian.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Preg-Icon-App-150x150.png" alt="" width="65" height="65" srcset="https://hesperian.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Preg-Icon-App-150x150.png 150w, https://hesperian.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Preg-Icon-App.png 234w" sizes="(max-width: 65px) 100vw, 65px" /></a><strong> in English <em>and</em> Spanish! </strong>Hesperian’s award-winning <em>Safe Pregnancy and Birth</em> app for <a href="http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/safe-pregnancy-and-birth/id496919735?mt=8">iPhone</a> and <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.hesperian.safepregnancyandbirth">Android </a>presents life-saving information using clear language, step-by step instructions, and illustrations. If you don’t have a smart phone, you can <a href="/books-and-resources/safe-pregnancy-and-birth-mobile-app/%20">preview the app online</a>.</p>
<h2>A Way to Create and Share Health Materials</h2>
<p><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-8867" title="materials_exchange_simple" src="https://hesperian.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/materials_exchange_simple1.png" alt="" width="65" height="61" />Have you created your own materials using Hesperian text or images? Share your materials with us at <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#d0b8b5a3a0b5a2b9b1be90b8b5a3a0b5a2b9b1befebfa2b7"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="95fdf0e6e5f0e7fcf4fbd5fdf0e6e5f0e7fcf4fbbbfae7f2">[email&#160;protected]</span></span></a> and help us build an online resource library! See our <a title="Open Copyright" href="/about/open-copyright/">open copyright policy</a>.</p>
<h2>… And more coming soon</h2>
<ul>
<li>More language hubs</li>
<li>Additional books in the HealthWiki</li>
<li><em>Safe Pregnancy and Birth</em> app in additional languages and accessible for lower end phones</li>
<li>Animated video content</li>
</ul>
<p>Write to us at <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="365e53454653445f5758765e53454653445f575818594451">[email&#160;protected]</a></span> to learn more, and please consider <a href="http://store.hesperian.org/HB/prod/EXTERNAL.html">making a donation</a> to support this initiative!</p>
